  "body": "1. create a group chat with some contact\r\n2. as second contact, accept the invitation so both of you are in a group seeing the incoming messages\r\n3. send several messages to a group as admin\r\n4. as admin, remove second participant from a group\r\n5. as admin , add the same participant back again\r\n\r\nAs a result for second participant, the group chat page says he has joined, but invitation to join is not shown , also he is not able to post anything to this group\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1012\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-27 at 15 57 02\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/119831051-8d390c80-bf05-11eb-83ea-28cbf7c2b9fd.png\">\r\n",
